<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT6">
<l>mūvaril mutalva ṉāya voruvaṉai yulakaṅ koṇṭa</l>
<l>kōviṉaik kuṭantai mēya kurumaṇit tiraḷai yiṉpap</l>
<l>pāviṉaip paccait tēṉaip paimpoṉṉai yamarar ceṉṉip</l>
<l>pūviṉaip pukaḻun toṇṭa reñcollip pukaḻvar tāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The One who became first among Three, the king who took the world,</l>
<l>Cluster of bluestone gems who dwells in Kuṭantai, song of delight,</l>
<l>Fresh honey, finest gold, flower on the celestials’ heads -</l>
<l>What do His servants who praise [him] say in praise?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
